file_content.text: What do you think the Esh-kha are like? I can't wait to meet one.
Talking to ancient Jedi masters? You get to have all the fun.
I wonder if anything about Blaesus was real.
You will protect the royal family, won't you?
I can't imagine Hoth. I've never seen more than a few flakes of snow.
Sorry if I... surprised you, back on Attis Station. I didn't know how to explain.
Come on! We can't let those Imperials trample all over our station.
The ship will feel strange when Tai's gone. But, Balmorra needs him more.
Thank you, for saving us from the Sith. I'm sorry I wasn't much help.
I used to dream about flying through space.
